data.description: This is your opportunity to own a beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the San Salito community in St. Augustine. The home features stucco and ledgestone front, granite counters, bay window in the master bedroom, crown molding, california bar top, and stainless steel appliances. This floorplan includes a separate living room/dining room combination, eat-in kitchen, family room, split bedrooms, 3-car garage and a enclosed porch overlooking a beautiful conservation area. The master bedroom is light and bright with a bay window for your reading nook, watching the wildlife in the back yard or just relaxing! Master bedroom has a tray ceiling and features double walk-in closets! The three other bedrooms are generous sizes including one with another walk-in closet. San Salito is a beautiful Mediterranean-style community nestled just off SR 16 on Woodlawn Road. Conveniently located minutes from Historic St. Augustine, Vilano Beach and I-95, with fantastic shopping, restaurants and highly desirable St. Johns county schools. Residents will enjoy amazing amenities such as an expansive pool with kid's splash area, clubhouse, fitness center, playground, tennis/pickle ball and volleyball courts.
